    rating: "Pretty Bad"
    comments: "The dialogue was incrediblely Wes Anderson but was not really interesting at all, the jokes were incredibly meta/non-sequitor, the symbolism was really faint and not really that compelling as a message, the foreshadowing was present but was also predictable"
  }
